OL,3,C'Emergency' as number of butterflies
OL,4,Cin Wales lowest on record, warns
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FThe number of butterflies in Wales is
OL,8,Fthe lowest on record, a wildlife
OL,9,Fcharity has warned.
OL,11,FButterfly Conservation has declared a
OL,12,Fnational 'Butterfly Emergency', after
OL,13,Fresults of its Big Butterfly Count
OL,14,Fshowed a decline in numbers of the
OL,15,Finsect.
OL,17,FThe 2024 Count saw the lowest number
OL,18,Fof butterflies spotted in Wales per
OL,19,FCount in its 14-year history
