OL,3,C'Emergency' as number of butterflies
OL,4,Cin Wales lowest on record, warns
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FMore than 9,000 Big Butterfly Counts
OL,8,Facross the UK reported not seeing a
OL,9,Fsingle butterfly.
OL,11,FIn total, 85% of species counted in
OL,12,FWales showed a decline in numbers
OL,13,Fcompared with 2023.
OL,15,FThe Red Admiral species showed the
OL,16,Fgreatest country level decline, down
OL,17,F86% on last year.
OL,19,FIn total, there were 40,535
OL,20,Fbutterflies spotted in Wales, down
OL,21,Fmore than 22,000 or 36% on 2023.
