OL,3,C'Emergency' as number of butterflies
OL,4,Cin Wales lowest on record, warns
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FDr Richard Fox, Head of Science at
OL,8,FButterfly Conservation, said: "The
OL,9,Fresults are in line with wider
OL,10,Fevidence that the summer of 2024 has
OL,11,Fbeen very poor for butterflies.
OL,13,F"Butterflies are a key indicator
OL,14,Fspecies; when they are in trouble we
OL,15,Fknow that the wider environment is in
OL,16,Ftrouble too.
