OL,3,C'Emergency' as number of butterflies
OL,4,Cin Wales lowest on record, warns
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,F"Nature is sounding the alarm call. We
OL,8,Fmust act now if we are to turn the
OL,9,Ftide on these rapid declines and
OL,10,Fprotect species for future
OL,11,Fgenerations."
OL,13,FMore than 85,000 'citizen scientists'
OL,14,Ftook part in Butterfly Conservation's
OL,15,FBig Butterfly Count this year,
OL,16,Fsubmitting 143,241 Counts.
OL,18,FIn Wales, a total of 6,417 Counts were
OL,19,Fsubmitted by 4,586 people.
